HNode.Name: WEB_SALES
HNode.SQLDefinition:
CREATE TABLE WEB_SALES (
WS_ITEM_SK VARCHAR(25) NOT NULL,
WS_WAREHOUSE_SK VARCHAR(25) , WS_PROMO_SK VARCHAR(25) , WS_ORDER_NUMBER VARCHAR(25) NOT NULL,
PRIMARY KEY (WS_ITEM_SK, WS_ORDER_NUMBER) );

HNode.Name: Q1
HNode.SQLDefinition: SELECT * FROM CATALOG_SALES, DATE_DIM WHERE D_YEAR = 2000 AND D_MOY = 7 AND CS_SOLD_DATE_SK = D_DATE_SK AND CS_ITEM_SK IN (SELECT I_ITEM_SK FROM FREQUENT_SS_ITEMS) AND CS_BILL_CUSTOMER_SK IN (SELECT C_CUSTOMER_SK FROM BEST_SS_CUSTOMER)

HNode.Name: DATE_DIM
HNode.SQLDefinition:
CREATE TABLE DATE_DIM ( D_DATE_SK VARCHAR(25) NOT NULL,
D_DATE VARCHAR(25) ,
D_WEEK_SEQ VARCHAR(25) ,
D_YEAR VARCHAR(25) ,
D_MOY VARCHAR(25) ,
D_QOY VARCHAR(25) ,
PRIMARY KEY (D_DATE_SK) );

HNode.Name: FREQUENT_SS_ITEMS
HNode.SQLDefinition: CREATE VIEW FREQUENT_SS_ITEMS AS SELECT I_ITEM_DESC, I_ITEM_SK, D_DATE SOLDDATE, COUNT(*) CNT FROM STORE_SALES, DATE_DIM, ITEM WHERE SS_SOLD_DATE_SK = D_DATE_SK AND SS_ITEM_SK = I_ITEM_SK AND D_YEAR IN (2000,2001,2002,2003) GROUP BY I_ITEM_DESC, I_ITEM_SK, D_DATE;

HNode.Name: ITEM
CUSTOMER
BEST_SS_CUSTOMER
HNode.SQLDefinition: CREATE VIEW BEST_SS_CUSTOMER AS SELECT C_CUSTOMER_SK FROM STORE_SALES, CUSTOMER WHERE SS_CUSTOMER_SK = C_CUSTOMER_SK GROUP BY C_CUSTOMER_SK;

CREATE TABLE STORE_RETURNS ( SR_RETURNED_DATE_SK VARCHAR(25) ,
SR_ITEM_SK VARCHAR(25) NOT NULL,
SR_TICKET_NUMBER VARCHAR(25) NOT NULL, SR_RETURN_QUANTITY VARCHAR(25) ,
PRIMARY KEY (SR_ITEM_SK, SR_TICKET_NUMBER) );

HNode.Name: CATALOG_SALES
HNode.SQLDefinition:
CREATE TABLE CATALOG_SALES ( CS_SOLD_DATE_SK VARCHAR(25) ,
CS_BILL_CUSTOMER_SK VARCHAR(25) ,
CS_ITEM_SK VARCHAR(25) NOT NULL,
CS_ORDER_NUMBER VARCHAR(25) NOT NULL,
PRIMARY KEY (CS_ITEM_SK, CS_ORDER_NUMBER) );

HNode.Name: STORE_SALES
HNode.SQLDefinition:
CREATE TABLE STORE_SALES ( SS_SOLD_DATE_SK VARCHAR(25) ,
SS_ITEM_SK VARCHAR(25) NOT NULL, SS_CUSTOMER_SK VARCHAR(25) ,
SS_ADDR_SK VARCHAR(25) ,
SS_TICKET_NUMBER VARCHAR(25) NOT NULL,
SS_EXT_SALES_PRICE DECIMAL(7,2) ,
PRIMARY KEY (SS_ITEM_SK, SS_TICKET_NUMBER) );
